1.  Information for W32 Chipset Users

XF86_W32 has been discontinued as of XFree86-4.0, since all of its functions
(and more) are now included in the SVGA server XF86_SVGA.  All necessary infor-
mation on using Tseng chips with XF86_SVGA is provided in README.tseng

